title: SanDisk 16GB Micro SDHC Memory Card with SD Adapter w/USB High Speed SDHC/SDXC & MicroSDHC/MicroSDXC Card Reader
description: SanDisk microSD 16GB mobile memory cards are the ideal companion for casual phone users because they plug directly into the phone providing immediate expansion of memory storage needed for carrying more music and photos. Designed for ease of sharing your latest music downloads and fun pics with your friends. Includes High Speed USB SDHC/SDHXC & MicroSDHC/MicroSDXC Card reader for use with your computer.
